@node "EDITO" "eDiTORiAL!"
@toc "MAIN"

 @{"MAIN MENU" LINK "MAIN"}


                   [======( k-RaD & eLiTE #2 )======]

                [=====( iSSUE #2 - April 21st'95 )=====]

               [=====( THE *REAL* SCOOP ON THE SCENE )=====]


 [RaJ!'s first words] :

OHello all!!!! Glad to see me back with another edition of this
 humble mag of the pir8? hehe... i added something new this time around,
 a UTILS section.... alot of guys said "hey asshole include utils too"
 so i gave in to the readership and added it in... happily it will make
 you readers feel better and make this small shit text file bigger hehe
 the points system is still very new and testy, so all you groups do not
 rag on about the points :))... if something was missed please tell me
 and it will be rightfully added to the proceding issue (can't catch it
 all hahaa)... as well i would like to welcome a dude who will now be a
 partner in crime for this mag with me: fLAShbACk!/tRSi/rEDNEX!,
 heheh a dude that most of the people who know me, know we have been very
 naughty at each others throats... differences have been set aside and
 past as well hehe... welcome aboard dude!... well if ya like what ya
 read in the first issue, read on you k-radula'd scene dudes... !

 P.S. a reminder for some of you hate peoples (heh)... this mag is not
      in any way biased or discriminatory (phew) towards any group, all
      are judged and looked upon fairly in the releases game :)) if ya
      don't like me to rag on your release, don't release shit hehe

 P.P.S. The Utils section was born on the 27th of march.

 P.P.P.S. NOW BACK TO HAVING FUN... !


                                   -*-*-


    hERE wE gO! tHiS iS tHE sECOND iSSUE oF k-RaD & eLiTE diSK mAG. tHERE
    hAS bEEN sOME dRASTiC cHANGES tO tHE oRiGANAL diSK mAG (issue 1) aS
    yOU cAN sEE. wE hOPE tHESE cHANGES aRE fOR tHE beST, aND wE hOPE yOU
    eNJOY tHE nEW fORMAT iN wHiCH iS gOiNG tO bE uSED fOR eACH diSK mAG.
    tHERE aRE aLSO gOiNG tO bE a aHANGE iN tHE mUZAK uSED eVERY mONTH tO
    mAKE tHiS mAG nOT tHE sAME tHiNG mONTH aFTER mONTH. sO wE hOPE yOU
    liKE tHiS diSK mAG! aND tHANKS fOR tAKEN tHE tiME tO viEW tHiS nOTE!
    sO sORRY fOR bORiNG tHE hELL oUTTA yOU! hEHEHE, gO viEW tHE mAG!

